### 🔍 Problem kahan hai?

Maine aapko jo JSON diya tha, usme ek choti si technical mismatch ho gayi hai. Aapke **ChannelModel.kt** mein photo ke liye variable ka naam `logo` hai, lekin mere JSON mein maine use `thumbnail` likh diya tha. Is wajah se app confusion mein aa gayi.

